{"id":529453,"date":[{"year":1973,"month":7,"day":29}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"152","ytitle":"","mtitle":"农场速写","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>劼音</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟华</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>钟华　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劼音　画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\07\\737t040501.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>朝霞飞进茅草棚，“愿如秧苗浴风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小将评书抒心声:农场沃土扎深根。”</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\07\\737t040502.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>土满车呵泥满筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同豪情垒堤上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗洒千吨何所惜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中稻花千里香。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\07\\737t040503.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>广播室，天地大，笑驾春风传喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海风云容得下。心随音波飞天涯。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1973\\07\\737t040504.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“双抢”前夕忙机修，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔壮志催铁牛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈开泥浪连天涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵来粮山庆丰收。</FONT>"}]}